  "response": "Not all questions on Quora receive answers. While many questions do get responses due to the platform's large and diverse user base, some may remain unanswered. This can happen for various reasons, such as a question being too niche, unclear, or lacking enough information to attract answers. Additionally, users may choose not to answer if they feel they lack expertise on the topic. However, popular or well-formulated questions are more likely to receive attention and responses.",
